item.description:
Three days till E-Day.
Once the polls close, it's out of our hands. After all the hard work and cash we've all spent to help get our local liberty candidates elected, win, lose, or draw, we'll want to drink beer. That and enjoy some deliciously prepared food and enjoy each others company. So please, join us at the Forsythe residence after the polls close on election day for a warm and cordial gathering. Although there will be food and drink, it never hurts to bring a little more.
item.name: Election Day After Polls Close, After Hours Party
